- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper involves building a convolutional neural network for prediction. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the impact of the prediction on patient safety and medication reconciliation process. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper involves predicting medication regimens based on pharmacological correlations among medications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques for prediction.
